00:00:25.840 --> 00:00:30.000
Boiled Potato - 3  . Mash the boiled potato

00:00:30.200 --> 00:00:32.520
Big Onion - 1

00:00:32.520 --> 00:00:33.020
Curry Leaves - Little

00:00:33.180 --> 00:00:36.000
Green Chilli - 3 .Slit them into halves , as shown in the video

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:42.500
Grated Ginger  - Little ( optional)

00:00:43.620 --> 00:00:46.100
For Seasoning :  Red Chilli - 2

00:00:48.600 --> 00:00:49.100
Mustard Seeds - 1/4 tsp  , Cumin Seeds (Jeera) - 1/2 tsp

00:00:50.500 --> 00:00:54.720
Urad Dal - 1/4 tsp , Bengal Gram Dal (Kadalai Paruppu) - 1 tsp

00:00:54.720 --> 00:00:56.200
Turmeric Powder , Asafotedia

00:00:57.900 --> 00:00:59.440
Heat about 3-4 tsp of oil

00:00:59.440 --> 00:01:03.900
Once heated season it with Urad Dal , Bengal Gram Dal.

00:01:07.580 --> 00:01:11.340
Once it starts to splutter , add mustard seeds and jeera.

00:01:13.180 --> 00:01:14.220
Add Red Chilli .

00:01:22.420 --> 00:01:27.300
I missed to mention cashew nuts in the ingredients. Now add few of the nuts.Cut them into small pieces

00:01:32.940 --> 00:01:37.780
Now add the finely sliced big onion and curry leaves

00:01:50.300 --> 00:01:51.740
Finely grated ginger

00:01:56.120 --> 00:01:58.820
Saute it well until the onions turn golden brown.

00:02:00.760 --> 00:02:01.880
Add salt to taste

00:02:07.860 --> 00:02:09.700
Add the slit green chillies

00:02:16.080 --> 00:02:18.560
Add Turmeric powder and asafotedia.

00:02:30.480 --> 00:02:31.920
Add the mashed potato

00:02:38.260 --> 00:02:42.420
Mash the potato in such a way that one or two pieces are left out.

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:57.960
Add very little water . The onions should not be over cooked , the crunchy effect of the onion tastes good.

00:03:03.640 --> 00:03:05.800
Allow it to boil for about 5 mins.

00:03:09.160 --> 00:03:10.360
The Poori Kizhangu Masala / Potato Curry is ready !!!

00:03:11.060 --> 00:03:12.520
The Flavor and aroma of the ginger increases the taste of the recipe

00:03:13.480 --> 00:03:14.480
Add chopped coriander leaves

00:03:18.760 --> 00:03:21.000
Tasty Poori Kizhangu Masala is ready !! Enjoy with hot Poori

